SHERPASURFING is an open source Cyber Security Solution

Netflow is an aggregation of network packet traffic. Silk is a netflow generator that is open source and free. The ddl provided in sherpa surfing is based on silk netflow but can be used with other sensors and even ipaudit.

Silk can be found at:

http://tools.netsa.cert.org/silk/

The silk configuration file is provided as an example